{"tid":32304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾鈺成稱重新考慮是否參選","createTime":"2016-12-10T06:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T06:17:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a7d45f023b01da44efd2e098f59236572225dff","tid":32304,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】立法會前主席曾鈺成對行政長官梁振英處境表示同情，認為他作了負責任的決定。曾鈺成又表示會重新考慮是否需要出選特首。<br />\n<br />\n立法會前主席曾鈺成對梁振英宣布不角逐連任深表婉惜，並祝福梁振英的家人。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成承認梁振英不參選令他要重新考慮是否需要出選特首。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日有不同消息指中央打了紅燈，不贊成他入閘，他說不知道消息從何而來。他形容自已還沒到路口，交通燈是甚麼顏色，對他來說沒有意義。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=203347&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D203347%26home%3D1&d=8OOtnlwkX6z87RSpQSFzpwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=9ed9e2ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D203347%26home%3D1&h=66d49f96\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=203347&amp;home=1</a>"},{"pid":"01c7602dddf6f45fde41be7f93eeecf5a532a141","tid":32304,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"老鼠：你個阿爺係咩個呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}